test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (4 == 3)
 +  where 4 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7fa925502fc0>([-5])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7fa925502fc0> = [[1, -5], [1, -5, 1], [-5], [-5, 1], [1, -5], [1, -5, 1], ...].count
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 5 == -5
 +  where 5 = <built-in function prod>([-1, -5])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
